  "about": {
    "heading": "About",
    "creditsButtonLabel": "Full theatre credits",
    "paragraphs": [
      "proxydite (Ryan Samuel Davies) is a Welsh video and sound artist, creative technologist, and theatre video designer based in Swansea. His practice reflects a staunch belief in nature as both sustainer of life and healer of soul, envisioning a harmony between decentralised tech and the wild.",
      "In his spare time, Ryan is a writer and filmmaker, exploring stories that echo his roots and convictions."
    ]
  },
